Package view

Class FilterObj

java.lang.Object
view.FilterObj
public class FilterObj extends Object
The FilterObj class is used to filter what details to print in a report. It allows users to specify which information should be included in the report by selecting or deselecting various filtering options.
Since:
2023-11-13
